<P>
TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Hey, scumbags, get out of my courtroom. You're all guilty." 
</P>
<P>
A frustrated Superior Court Judge Michael Tynan, who dismissed a case against 
three men allegedly caught with 10 kilograms of cocaine because the Sheriff's 
Department refused to provide documents about its investigation of five 
suspended narcotics officers who are key witnesses. 
</P>
