DEFENSE INITIATIVE; SPACE WARFARE; SPACE WEAPONS; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID 
-- SOUTH KOREA; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES; STEALTH BOMBER 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
