<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
MERGERS; BANKING INDUSTRY -- SOUTHERN UNITED STATES; CITIZENS &amp; SOUTHERN 
CORP; SOVRAN FINANCIAL CORP; AVANTOR FINANCIAL CORP 
</P>
